net.dv8tion.jda.core.hooks

Class ListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dv8tion.jda.core.hooks.ListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener

    public abstract class ListenerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements EventListener
    An abstract implementation of EventListener which divides Events for you.

    Example: 

    
 public class MyReadyListener extends ListenerAdapter
 {
     @Override
     public void onReady(ReadyEvent event)
     {
         System.out.println("I am ready to go!");
     }

     @Override
     public void onMessageReceived(MessageReceivedEvent event)
     {
         System.out.printf("[%s]: %s\n", event.getAuthor().getName(), event.getMessage().getContentDisplay());
     }
 }
    See Also:
    EventListener, InterfacedEventManager
